()Role Risk kya hai?
Role Risk = kisi role ke permissions ki wajah se security ya compliance risk.

Example:-
Example 1 (High Risk Role)
Role: Finance Admin
Permissions:
- Read Financial Data
- Modify Financial Data
- Delete Financial Records

Yeh role high risk hai kyunki user:-
data dekh sakta hai
data change kar sakta hai
data delete bhi kar sakta hai
Agar misuse ho gaya to financial fraud ho sakta hai.

Example 2 (Low Risk Role):-
Role: Finance Viewer
Permissions:-
- Read Financial Data
Yeh low risk role hai kyunki sirf read access hai.
-----------------
()Role Risk ke common reasons:-
1️⃣ Sensitive Permissions:-
Example:-
Delete Database
Approve Payments
Modify Payroll

2️⃣ Segregation of Duties (SoD) Conflict:-
Agar ek hi role me conflicting permissions ho.
Example:-
Create Vendor
Approve Vendor Payment
Ye dangerous hai kyunki ek hi person fraud kar sakta hai.

3️⃣ Excess Privileges:-
Role me zarurat se zyada permissions ho.
Example:-
Developer Role:
- Read Code
- Deploy Code
- Delete Production Database

()SailPoint me roles ko risk score diya jata hai.
Example:-
Role	          Risk Level
Finance Viewer-----Low
HR Manager---------Medium
System Admin-------High

()Risk reduce kaise karte hain:-
1️⃣ Least Privilege follow karo
2️⃣ SoD policies use karo
3️⃣ Access review / certification karo
4️⃣ Time-bound access do
